Grace Mugabe.They want her to be prosecuted for allegedly assaulting
Mzansi model Gabriella Engels in a hotel room in August this year.The DA, Afriforum and the three rights groups, Freedom
Under Law, The Commission for Gender Equality and the Women’s Legal Centre
